---
---
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="relative min-h-[90vh] md:min-h-screen flex items-center w-full pt-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="/images/interlagos-aerial.jpg"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center filter brightness-[0.82] contrast-[1.1] saturate-[1.05]"
      id="hero-parallax-img"
      alt="Vista aérea do Autódromo de Interlagos"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-track-asphalt/85 via-track-asphalt/55 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-track-asphalt via-track-asphalt/35 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 shimmer-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative z-10 px-gutter w-full max-w-container-max mx-auto flex flex-col items-start justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 border border-primary/30 bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-sm animate-fade-up">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[16px]">verified</span>
        <span class="font-label-caps text-microcopy text-primary tracking-widest uppercase">Vagas limitadas · Processo de seleção</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-hero-headline-mobile md:font-hero-headline text-hero-headline-mobile md:text-hero-headline text-performance-white mb-6 uppercase animate-fade-up delay-100">
        Você vai pilotar<br /><span class="text-primary">em Interlagos.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-metallic-grey mb-10 max-w-2xl animate-fade-up delay-200">
        Um dia inteiro na pista mais icônica do Brasil. Ao lado de empresários que constroem negócios de alto nível.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-fade-up delay-300">
        <div class="inline-block p-4 -m-4 cursor-pointer" id="magnetic-wrapper">
          <a
            class="magnetic-btn justify-center items-center bg-podium-gold text-on-primary font-label-caps text-label-caps px-8 py-4 uppercase tracking-widest transition-all duration-300 animate-breathe btn-glow"
            href="#aplicacao"
            id="magnetic-element"
            style="transform: translate(0px, 0px);"
          >
            QUERO PARTICIPAR
          </a>
        </div>
        <a
          class="inline-flex justify-center items-center border border-metallic-grey/40 text-performance-white font-label-caps text-label-caps px-8 py-4 uppercase tracking-widest hover:border-performance-white hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300 mt-0 sm:ml-4"
          href="#experiencia"
        >
          CONHECER A EXPERIÊNCIA
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
